IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. TEST-MULTIMEDIA-LIB.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 AUDIO-PATH PIC X(256) VALUE "/path/to/audio.mp3".
01 VOLUME     PIC 9(3) VALUE 85.
01 RETURN-CODE PIC S9(4) COMP.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    CALL "COBOL_MOTSYS_SET_AUDIO_PATH" USING AUDIO-PATH RETURN-CODE.
    IF RETURN-CODE = 0 DISPLAY "Audio path set successfully: " AUDIO-PATH.

    CALL "COBOL_MOTSYS_SET_VOLUME" USING VOLUME RETURN-CODE.
    IF RETURN-CODE = 0 DISPLAY "Volume set to " VOLUME.

    CALL "COBOL_MOTSYS_PLAY_AUDIO" USING RETURN-CODE.
    IF RETURN-CODE = 0 DISPLAY "Audio playback started"
    ELSE DISPLAY "Playback failed. Error code: " RETURN-CODE.

    STOP RUN.
